## Without Docker Compose

```bash
# Build manually
docker build -t insightdrop-cli .

# Run (mount your local folders)
docker run --rm \
  -v $(pwd)/data:/app/data \
  -v $(pwd)/exports:/app/exports \
  insightdrop-cli generate

docker run --rm \
  -v $(pwd)/data:/app/data \
  -v $(pwd)/exports:/app/exports \
  insightdrop-cli analyze data/sales.csv

docker run --rm \
  -v $(pwd)/data:/app/data \
  -v $(pwd)/exports:/app/exports \
  insightdrop-cli export data/sales.csv --format pdf
```

